-- Bank of America Confirms Hire of UBS Banker Wilmot-Sitwell
-- B y   A m b e r e e n   C h o u d h u r y
-- 2012-04-25T08:40:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-25/bank-of-america-confirms-hire-of-ubs-banker-wilmot-sitwell.html
Bank of America Corp. (BAC)  said it hired
Alex Wilmot-Sitwell as president, Europe and Emerging markets
excluding Asia, the bank said in a memo to staff confirmed by a
spokesman.  Wilmot-Sitwell joins from  UBS AG. (UBSN)  He will be based in
London and will join in the coming months, the memo said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ambereen Choudhury in London at 
 achoudhury@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gavin Finch at 
 gfinch@bloomberg.net  